Further information
Our client, a leader in the Re-Insurance industry is seeking to hire multiple positions within their Catastrophe team.
If you have expertise in the areas of either Earthquake or Windstorm then our client wants to hear from you.
Working a senior level your role will involve providing expertise to upgrade existing models and also develop new models in conjunction with leading the risk management practice in your area of expertise.
Working right across the Asia-Pacific region the role will be varied and challenging whilst also providing candidates with a first class working culture and excellent promotion prospects.
